# Day 4 - Tuples and Sets

## Topics Learned

### Tuple
- ordered
- immutable
- allows duplicates

### Set
- unordered
- mutable
- unique values only

## Important Concepts

### Tuple vs List

Tuple:
- immutable
- faster
- safer for fixed data

List:
- mutable

### Why Sets Are Powerful

Sets provide:
- fast lookup
- duplicate removal
- intersection operations

## Real Data Engineering Use Cases

- remove duplicate customer IDs
- compare datasets
- fast membership checking
- unique record validation

