LeetCode 2 — Intersection of Two Arrays

File — intersection_arrays.py

class Solution:

    def intersection(self, nums1, nums2):

        return list(set(nums1) & set(nums2))


obj = Solution()

print(obj.intersection([1,2,2,1], [2,2]))

Output:

[2]


